{"tid":2431140,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"海防道舖30萬租出 跌價66%","createTime":"2021-03-03T12:03:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T12:03:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"db3320c5eb586c7767de31cea850cd80c7f49d3c","tid":2431140,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:03:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210303/XKKDXT3JG5EPHKDVXU76NNZ3SM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210303%2FXKKDXT3JG5EPHKDVXU76NNZ3SM%2F&d=UjOWczzRfTNgHoC3e3JiXzyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=1291c831\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210303%2FXKKDXT3JG5EPHKDVXU76NNZ3SM%2F&h=42d07d30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210303/XKKDXT3JG5EPHKDVXU76NNZ3SM/</a><br />\n<br />\n海防道舖30萬租出 跌價66%<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/zQG-XmlaYCf4c5SLZ-_Kte1ujr0=/960x720/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XMIYOCHUPNFATI6N2DLXL23M5M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FzQG-XmlaYCf4c5SLZ-_Kte1ujr0%3D%2F960x720%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXMIYOCHUPNFATI6N2DLXL23M5M.jpg&h=f1b1b3e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■尖沙嘴海防道最新有丟空逾一年的吉舖，以月租30萬元租出。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】受疫情「封關」影響，本港零售市道一蹶不振，導致不少核心區商舖租售價「插水」。尖沙嘴海防道屬旅客訪港購物熱點之一，該地段最新有丟空逾一年的吉舖以30萬元租出，比舊租大跌逾六成半。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n舖位已丟空逾一年<br />\n<br />\n鄰近港鐵站出口、海防道近彌敦道一帶屬當區一線地段，惟疫情下旅客人數大減，該地段亦吉舖連連，其中53至55號地下5號舖已丟空逾一年。據代理消息透露，上述舖位連入則閣，面積達1,900方呎，新近以30萬元租出，呎租約157元；較英國百年鞋履品牌Clarks早於2019年7月以88萬元承租，最新租金回落58萬元或約66%。<br />\n<br />\n至於毗鄰6B舖，面積約400方呎，最新亦市傳以約15萬元獲維特健靈租用，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n值得留意的是，維特健靈原於去年3月。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n工廈方面，中原工商舖梁錦和指，黃。。。。。。"}]}